FOD2DIE1 FOD2DIE1
FOD2DIE2 FOD2DIE2


$random Gore/HeadBounce { Gore/HeadBounce1 Gore/HeadBounce2 Gore/HeadBounce3 }
Gore/HeadBounce1 "Sounds/Monsters/Horrorspawn/HeadBounce1"
Gore/HeadBounce2 "Sounds/Monsters/Horrorspawn/HeadBounce2"
Gore/HeadBounce3 "Sounds/Monsters/Horrorspawn/HeadBounce3"

